The goal of the game is to strategically accelerate the car to reach the goal state on top of the right hill as quickly as possible. The episode ends if either the car reaches the goal position on top of the right hill or the length of the episode is 200.

The episode ends if either the car reaches the goal position on top of the right hill or the length of the episode is 200.

The episode ends if either the car reaches the goal position on top of the right hill or the length of the episode is 200.

The goal of the game is to strategically accelerate the car to reach the goal state on top of the right hill as quickly as possible. The episode ends if either the car reaches the goal position on top of the right hill or the length of the episode is 200.

The goal of the game is to strategically accelerate the car to reach the goal state on top of the right hill as quickly as possible. The episode ends if either the car reaches the goal position on top of the right hill or the length of the episode is 200.
